headline: MHS Health Wisconsin Earns Prestigious 4.5-Star NCQA Rating, Ranking Among Top 14 Medicaid Plans Nationwide
summary: MHS Health Wisconsin ("MHS Health"), one of Wisconsin's leading health maintenance organizations (HMOs) and a company of Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC), achieved a 4.5-Star rating from the National Committee for Quality Assurance (NCQA) and ranks among the top 14 Medicaid health plans nationwide. MHS Health is the only Medicaid HMO in Wisconsin to receive this distinction and the highest rating ever received by a Wisconsin Medicaid HMO for more than five years.
